  <!-- HERO SECTION --><section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
  <h1>Home &amp; Building Surveys in Tarvin</h1>
  <p>AssocRICS surveys with clear advice, fast turnaround, and a personal approach — trusted across Tarvin and Cheshire’s rural property market.</p>
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Get a Quick Quote</a>
  </div>
  </section><!-- MAIN CONTENT SECTION --><section class="service-detail">
  <div class="box-container">
  <h2>Independent Surveyor Covering Tarvin</h2>
  <p>
          Based near the Cheshire–Flintshire border, LEM Building Surveying Ltd provides expert home surveys across Tarvin and surrounding countryside villages. Whether you’re buying, selling or maintaining property, you’ll receive direct, clear advice from Liam — your qualified local AssocRICS surveyor.
        </p>
  <h2>Surveying Services in Tarvin</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 1 Home Survey:</strong> Basic condition check of newer or well-maintained properties. Traffic light ratings only — no advice.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 2 Home Survey:</strong> Ideal for most standard homes — includes condition ratings, maintenance advice, and repair recommendations.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 3 Building Survey:</strong> The most detailed report for older, extended, or non-standard homes — includes structure, defects, repair options, and optional costings.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Reports:</strong> Independent assessments for moisture, mould, or decay issues — ideal for mortgage lenders or peace of mind.</li>
  <li><strong>Measured Surveys &amp; Floorplans:</strong> Accurate internal plans for extensions, planning or space layout.</li>
  <li><strong>EPCs with Floorplans:</strong> Energy assessments plus marketing-ready layout plans — perfect for lettings and sales listings.</li>
  <li><strong>Ventilation Assessments:</strong> Identify condensation, mould or poor airflow risks and recommend appropriate improvements.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><a href="/services">View Full Range of Services →</a></p>
  <h2>Why Choose LEM?</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Cheshire Coverage:</strong> We regularly survey rural and village properties across Tarvin, Kelsall, Ashton, Waverton, and beyond.</li>
  <li><strong>No Sales Pitch:</strong> You deal directly with a surveyor — no agents or admin staff.</li>
  <li><strong>Quick Turnaround:</strong> Most surveys delivered in 3–5 working days.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Aligned:</strong> Surveys comply with the latest Home Survey Standard.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Book a Home Survey in Tarvin</h2>
  <p>
          Whether you’re buying a barn conversion or selling a family home in Tarvin, we’re happy to help. Get in touch for tailored, transparent advice and a fast quote.
        </p>
  <div class="cta-section">
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Request a Quote Now</a>
  <a class="secondary-button" href="/comparison">Compare Survey Levels</a>
  </div>
  </div>
  <RelatedAreas currentSlug={currentSlug} />
  </section><!-- FOOTER --><!-- Load Shared Header/Footer -->
